node.text:
Like bitter ash in his mouth, @chrisjerichofozzy submits to his rival @the_MJF. A soul-crushing moment for Chris Jericho & the entire stadium on #AEWDynamite.

Should it have ended this way?

node.title: MJF beats Chris Jericho - AEW Dynamite
